room_title: Escape room "Temple" by Xcape Room Fresno in Fresno
room_address: 3475 W Shaw Ave Suite #103 Fresno, California 93711
room_description:
King Kuhli could bare no children. He feared his family treasure would go to an undeserving heir. He designed the Temple of Scion to be inescapable unless the treasure was found. That way, only he could enter and leave, and all others would be trapped for eternity.
For hundreds of years, thousands of thieves and explorers alike have entered the temple, but none have come out. Can your team of explorers figure out the secrets of King Kuhli's Temple of Scion and find the treasure to escape?
